Others, they don't believe our explanation rumors, I only explain it here, it doesn't make sense to explain it elsewhere.

Over the years, the United States has launched a large-scale public opinion war.
To discredit China with many fake news, we do not want to explain these fake news.
Because: You can't wake a person who pretends to sleep.

But first of all, USA is not without smart people,
the American film in 2011: "Contagion"
https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1598778/

China, the United States, and the rest of the world are all experiencing what the film describes.
This movie is like a prophecy.
It also introduces the bat thing.
Even if you don't "eat" bats, the virus will spread from "pigs" to people!
These filmmakers know these things very well.
You better watch this movie, it is not difficult to find it online.

Recently, rumors say that the virus is because the Chinese eat bats.
They don't understand our Chinese culture, because the more educated people are, the more "dare" to eat bats.

Because the name of "bat", Chinese name is 蝙蝠.
蝠 is pronounced "fu", same pronunciation like 'foo'.
and '福' mean "happiness" and "blessing". and Blessing contains luck.
蝠 is pronounced the same as 福. You may see the same part on the right.
If charactor have same part, they sound the same 'foo'.
and 富 mean rich. but the 'sound' part in the bottom.

Also Chinese myth says that "white bats" can live for hundreds or thousands years. and It may become an immortal.
The most famous one is: Zhang Guolao（张果老）.
this is wikipedia link:
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zhang_Guolao

So the bat represents, wealth, lifespan, blessing.

And the decorations of ancient wooden doors and windows are engraved with bats. wish this house will get some good things.
The bat was carved on the wooden door of the royal palace in the Qing Dynasty.

So,
Eating bats will lose "blessing"!
Eating bats reduces lifespan!
Eating bats will lose "wealth"!
Who dares to eat bats?

Here's an introduction from Wikipedia:
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wufu

There are also introductions on the differences between bats in Chinese and Western cultures:
https://herschelian.wordpress.com/2018/04/18/why-the-chinese-are-batty-about-bats-and-westerners-are-not/

Or if you google for "Chinese culture bat", you can find many introductions about "bats" in China.

But rumors will not be eliminated because of truth. Many people now think that the Chinese "eat" bats and cause the virus.
I just explain to you the importance of "bats" in Chinese culture.
But No one will listen to my explanation.

The regions that eat the most bats are Southeast Asia, such as Indonesia.
